WEBVTT

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:24.500
"Love After Addiction"

00:01:24.600 --> 00:01:26.600
(Episode 11)

00:01:30.040 --> 00:01:30.719
For the variety show stuff

00:01:30.760 --> 00:01:31.935
I've already taken care of it.

00:01:31.959 --> 00:01:32.959
Don't worry, okay?

00:01:33.239 --> 00:01:34.840
They'll agree to re-edit.

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:35.959
About the persona,

00:01:36.040 --> 00:01:39.080
it'll also lean toward being authentic
and move toward a down-to-earth style.

00:01:40.200 --> 00:01:40.560
By the way,

00:01:41.200 --> 00:01:42.680
to prevent people from nitpicking,

00:01:43.280 --> 00:01:43.879
I think

00:01:43.880 --> 00:01:45.200
we can spend some money later

00:01:45.280 --> 00:01:46.480
to hire some villagers.

00:01:46.879 --> 00:01:48.000
Let them speak online.

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:49.280
Say nice things about you.

00:01:49.920 --> 00:01:51.560
Spend money to ward off trouble, I guess.

00:01:52.965 --> 00:01:54.775
Do we have to keep
deceiving people like this?

00:01:54.799 --> 00:01:55.799
Deceiving?

00:01:56.519 --> 00:01:57.519
Bro!

00:01:57.680 --> 00:01:58.760
Look at your situation now!

00:01:59.200 --> 00:01:59.879
People online are saying that

00:01:59.959 --> 00:02:01.359
you used the villagers for show!

00:02:01.799 --> 00:02:02.280
If we don't do it this way,

00:02:02.359 --> 00:02:03.759
how can I help clean up your image?

00:02:05.959 --> 00:02:07.000
What if they say again

00:02:07.120 --> 00:02:08.320
that you bribed the villagers?

00:02:08.719 --> 00:02:09.840
Never mind that.

00:02:10.199 --> 00:02:11.999
Deal with the present
first, we'll see later.

00:02:12.639 --> 00:02:13.639
There is no later.

00:02:14.120 --> 00:02:15.360
What do you mean, Yoki?

00:02:20.719 --> 00:02:21.879
Let's terminate the contract.

00:02:21.919 --> 00:02:22.919
What?

00:02:23.159 --> 00:02:24.159
Terminate the contract?

00:02:25.080 --> 00:02:26.080
Yoki,

00:02:26.719 --> 00:02:27.960
Do you think that integrity,

00:02:28.080 --> 00:02:28.680
perseverance

00:02:28.759 --> 00:02:29.439
can help you stand firm

00:02:29.479 --> 00:02:30.679
in the entertainment industry?

00:02:31.120 --> 00:02:31.599
Without Liang Hao,

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:33.520
would you have come this far?

00:02:40.840 --> 00:02:41.840
What do you mean?

00:02:46.800 --> 00:02:47.880
I really thank you so much.

00:02:49.479 --> 00:02:50.479
From now on,

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.320
I want to walk my own path.

00:02:54.400 --> 00:02:55.400
You,

00:03:00.719 --> 00:03:01.879
walk your own path.

00:03:08.479 --> 00:03:09.800
I'll let you walk your own path.

00:03:09.919 --> 00:03:11.280
You'll be nothing!

00:03:17.520 --> 00:03:19.199
Miss Fang.

00:03:19.719 --> 00:03:20.120
What?

00:03:20.719 --> 00:03:21.719
Big-shot agent Liang

00:03:21.800 --> 00:03:22.960
finally made up your mind?

00:03:24.120 --> 00:03:25.120
Yes, indeed.

00:03:25.360 --> 00:03:26.199
That Yoki guy

00:03:26.280 --> 00:03:27.600
doesn't know what's good for him.

00:03:27.879 --> 00:03:29.479
I warned you a long time ago,

00:03:30.199 --> 00:03:32.479
Yoki isn't
someone who takes orders obediently.

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:35.080
Then...

00:03:35.560 --> 00:03:36.199
Then from now on,

00:03:36.560 --> 00:03:37.439
Big-shot Agent Liang,

00:03:37.520 --> 00:03:38.640
please take good care of me!

00:03:39.840 --> 00:03:41.280
I'll prepare the contract.

00:03:41.560 --> 00:03:43.680
Looking forward to working together!

00:03:44.479 --> 00:03:45.519
As am I.

00:03:55.159 --> 00:03:56.159
Dad.

00:03:57.599 --> 00:03:58.599
Where have you been?

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.080
Just clearing my mind.

00:04:03.800 --> 00:04:04.800
If you don't want...

00:04:04.840 --> 00:04:05.920
I want to go back with you.

00:04:13.879 --> 00:04:14.879
Dad.

00:04:16.759 --> 00:04:17.759
I'm sorry.

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:26.120
Dad...

00:04:28.120 --> 00:04:30.000
For the past few years, it was me
who didn't spend time with you.

00:04:31.279 --> 00:04:32.279
I wasn't sensible enough.

00:04:35.959 --> 00:04:37.120
I won't be stubborn anymore.

00:04:40.480 --> 00:04:41.480
I'm sorry.

00:05:05.581 --> 00:05:07.956
(Lanwan Village Offices)

00:05:28.519 --> 00:05:29.519
Village chief.

00:05:29.920 --> 00:05:30.920
Sorry about yesterday.

00:05:31.079 --> 00:05:31.720
I didn't give an explanation

00:05:31.800 --> 00:05:32.800
to everyone right away.

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:35.720
No need to explain.

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:40.360
You,

00:05:40.519 --> 00:05:41.519
I know well enough.

00:05:46.240 --> 00:05:46.639
Village chief,

00:05:47.199 --> 00:05:47.959
this is the savings

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:49.280
I've accumulated over the years.

00:05:49.759 --> 00:05:50.759
Although it's not much,

00:05:51.480 --> 00:05:53.240
but I want to try my
best to make up for it.

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:54.560
It's all been resolved.

00:05:55.720 --> 00:05:58.160
Yoki has already covered all the money.

00:06:04.000 --> 00:06:05.000
Just sign here,

00:06:05.399 --> 00:06:07.360
consider it as everyone borrowing from you.

00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:11.360
The village got involved because of me,

00:06:12.439 --> 00:06:13.680
I should bear this loss!

00:06:14.879 --> 00:06:15.879
Yoki,

00:06:16.480 --> 00:06:17.839
you make this old face of mine

00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:18.920
have no place to hide.

00:06:20.352 --> 00:06:21.959
Everyone, in their hearts

00:06:22.040 --> 00:06:23.040
feels uneasy too.

00:06:23.879 --> 00:06:25.000
It's okay, village chief!

00:06:28.879 --> 00:06:29.879
How about this?

00:06:29.959 --> 00:06:31.199
I'll kneel to you, okay?

00:06:31.639 --> 00:06:32.199
No, no, no!

00:06:32.439 --> 00:06:32.959
Will you sign or not, village chief?

00:06:33.120 --> 00:06:34.615
Village chief, will you
sign or not? Get up.

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:35.639
Okay, okay, fine.

00:06:36.079 --> 00:06:37.079
I'll sign!

00:06:37.199 --> 00:06:38.199
I'll sign!

00:06:39.519 --> 00:06:40.519
My waist, oh!

00:06:40.720 --> 00:06:41.720
Hurry up and sign!

00:07:33.600 --> 00:07:35.279
This is the IOU we signed with him.

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:37.600
Why don't you take a look?

00:07:41.120 --> 00:07:42.120
Really won't look.

00:07:45.560 --> 00:07:46.560
I think

00:07:47.079 --> 00:07:48.279
you still need to take a look.

00:07:49.272 --> 00:07:50.408
If you won't look, then don't.

00:07:50.439 --> 00:07:51.639
It's just an IOU.

00:07:52.160 --> 00:07:53.160
Then I'll keep it.

00:07:55.680 --> 00:07:56.680
Village chief.

00:07:57.000 --> 00:07:58.200
You keep it yourself properly.

00:07:59.120 --> 00:07:59.519
His matters

00:07:59.639 --> 00:08:00.719
have nothing to do with me.

00:09:53.519 --> 00:09:55.240
Go, say goodbye to Grandma.

00:10:04.360 --> 00:10:05.360
Grandma.

00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:07.800
I've troubled you these years.

00:10:08.679 --> 00:10:09.679
No need to say more.

00:11:32.399 --> 00:11:33.519
These things,

00:11:34.039 --> 00:11:36.159
I'll keep them for you.

00:11:57.320 --> 00:11:58.320
Goodbye.

00:11:59.519 --> 00:12:00.519
Never see you again.

00:12:10.360 --> 00:12:12.255
The agent of the newly
crowned film emperor Yoki.

00:12:12.279 --> 00:12:12.799
Breaking news:

00:12:13.039 --> 00:12:13.919
Well-known actor Yoki

00:12:13.920 --> 00:12:15.600
