00:12:15.720 --> 00:12:16.759
Yoki has long been taking

00:12:16.799 --> 00:12:17.799
psychiatric medication,

00:12:17.919 --> 00:12:19.759
which constituting a
major breach of contract.

00:12:20.600 --> 00:12:21.440
Well-known actor Yoki

00:12:21.559 --> 00:12:22.799
auctioned his luxury residence.

00:12:23.519 --> 00:12:25.296
Fang Xiaotian supports
multiple left-behind children

00:12:25.320 --> 00:12:26.360
and taking care of

00:12:26.440 --> 00:12:27.936
a seventy-year-old solitary
elderly person long-term.

00:12:27.960 --> 00:12:29.280
The final copyright fee soared to

00:12:29.320 --> 00:12:30.600
72 million yuan,

00:12:30.799 --> 00:12:32.799
setting a new record for

00:12:32.879 --> 00:12:33.480
non-fiction female narratives.

00:12:33.480 --> 00:12:34.000
Stock price of Haotian
Entertainment Company

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:35.679
surged with heavy volume today.

00:12:35.960 --> 00:12:36.720
Can you talk about your

00:12:36.759 --> 00:12:37.519
upcoming work arrangements

00:12:37.520 --> 00:12:38.576
after signing with Haotian Entertainment？

00:12:38.600 --> 00:12:39.279
Mr. Liang used to be

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:40.200
Yoki's agent,

00:12:40.200 --> 00:12:40.840
are you really not bothered?

00:12:41.120 --> 00:12:42.279
I'm a simple person.

00:12:42.840 --> 00:12:43.840
Since I've chosen,

00:12:43.960 --> 00:12:45.279
I'll trust unconditionally.

00:12:45.840 --> 00:12:47.680
Everything follows the
company's arrangements.

00:12:48.080 --> 00:12:48.639
So now,

00:12:48.639 --> 00:12:49.440
have you moved past

00:12:49.480 --> 00:12:50.600
the shadow of that incident?

00:12:53.080 --> 00:12:54.080
People

00:12:54.279 --> 00:12:55.279
all have feelings,

00:12:55.799 --> 00:12:56.799
and need time.

00:12:57.480 --> 00:12:59.399
I'll resume work as soon as possible.

00:12:59.799 --> 00:13:01.399
May I ask your view on Yoki's
current condition?

00:13:01.799 --> 00:13:02.320
Sorry,

00:13:02.399 --> 00:13:03.559
that question is not okay,

00:13:03.600 --> 00:13:04.200
change to another,

00:13:04.320 --> 00:13:05.320
okay?

00:13:05.399 --> 00:13:07.480
I hope no more girls

00:13:07.919 --> 00:13:09.159
have the same experience as me.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:10.279
We have other matters later.

00:13:10.399 --> 00:13:11.399
Sorry.

00:13:11.614 --> 00:13:13.120
Then can you talk about
something that we like?

00:13:13.159 --> 00:13:14.720
Absolutely not relying on men,

00:13:14.840 --> 00:13:16.040
And not relying on you either?

00:13:16.600 --> 00:13:17.600
You, aren't you a man?

00:13:18.000 --> 00:13:19.038
Which eye sees me

00:13:19.039 --> 00:13:20.039
not as a man?

00:13:20.080 --> 00:13:21.135
Which newspaper are you from?

00:13:21.159 --> 00:13:22.336
Believe it or not, I'll sue you!

00:13:22.360 --> 00:13:23.159
Oh my god!

00:13:23.200 --> 00:13:23.879
Let's go, let's go, let's go.

00:13:24.039 --> 00:13:25.039
Finally,

00:13:26.720 --> 00:13:27.240
I want to confess something

00:13:27.320 --> 00:13:28.320
to everyone:

00:13:31.279 --> 00:13:32.600
my sexual orientation is...

00:13:36.320 --> 00:13:37.320
[I'm attracted to] men.

00:13:46.200 --> 00:13:47.200
Very sorry.

00:13:48.080 --> 00:13:49.080
I announce,

00:13:50.519 --> 00:13:51.320
I will indefinitely withdrawal from

00:13:51.321 --> 00:13:52.401
the entertainment industry.

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:45.079
Fang Xiaotian, hailed by
netizens as the "Anti-Scum Warrior"

00:14:45.080 --> 00:14:46.319
has had her core victimhood narrative

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:48.678
