post-production synthesized audio.

00:14:52.879 --> 00:14:53.879
Yoki's face was digitally swapped

00:14:53.880 --> 00:14:55.080
using AI deepfake technology.

00:14:55.360 --> 00:14:56.398
Fang's domestic violence medical diagnosis

00:14:56.399 --> 00:14:57.519
has also been proven fake.

00:14:57.720 --> 00:14:58.839
Internal hospital records leaked

00:14:58.840 --> 00:15:00.278
revealing the real registration slip.

00:15:00.279 --> 00:15:02.398
That day, she only visited
the Plastic Surgery department

00:15:02.399 --> 00:15:03.399
for a consultation on
mandibular angle reduction,

00:15:03.399 --> 00:15:04.279
with no registration record

00:15:04.280 --> 00:15:05.439
at the ENT department whatsoever.

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:07.558
The hospital's PR department
has launched an investigation.

00:15:07.559 --> 00:15:08.638
If the official seal is proven forged,

00:15:08.639 --> 00:15:10.759
the case will be handed
over to judicial authorities.

00:15:13.200 --> 00:15:14.200
Fabricated!

00:15:14.360 --> 00:15:15.799
All of it is fabricated!

00:15:16.000 --> 00:15:17.015
At the cost of his own withdrawal

00:15:17.039 --> 00:15:18.296
to expose your previous recording with him.

00:15:18.320 --> 00:15:19.320
Is that also fabricated?

00:15:19.360 --> 00:15:20.400
Of course it's fabricated!

00:15:20.519 --> 00:15:22.000
All of this is fabricated!

00:15:22.159 --> 00:15:22.679
You and Fang Xiaotian

00:15:22.679 --> 00:15:23.679
really settled privately?

00:15:23.840 --> 00:15:24.519
Is this really you

00:15:24.519 --> 00:15:25.000
who orchestrated it?

00:15:25.000 --> 00:15:25.519
Let me tell you,

00:15:25.759 --> 00:15:26.360
all of this is

00:15:26.440 --> 00:15:27.159
AI synthesized.

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:29.440
Pure nonsense.

00:15:29.720 --> 00:15:30.600
Please answer directly!

00:15:30.720 --> 00:15:31.360
Please answer directly!

00:15:31.679 --> 00:15:32.320
Miss Fang!

00:15:32.320 --> 00:15:33.320
Miss Fang, Miss Fang!

00:15:33.440 --> 00:15:34.560
Is it really all fabricated?

00:15:34.679 --> 00:15:35.679
Is it really like that?

00:15:35.840 --> 00:15:37.039
Can you respond us?

00:15:37.440 --> 00:15:37.919
Did you really reach

00:15:37.920 --> 00:15:39.000
a private agreement?

00:15:39.080 --> 00:15:39.559
Miss Fang.

00:15:39.559 --> 00:15:40.480
Miss Fang, answer the question.

00:15:40.481 --> 00:15:41.559
Miss Fang, Miss Fang!

00:15:41.799 --> 00:15:42.799
Please stay a moment!

00:16:49.408 --> 00:16:51.715
(One Year Later)

00:17:06.759 --> 00:17:07.400
If everyone

00:17:07.401 --> 00:17:08.559
wants to buy souvenirs,

00:17:08.640 --> 00:17:09.519
you can go to the

